OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShoplifter: Police need to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstop people like me        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A persistent shoplifter has said the   
OL,6, police need to do more to stop people  
OL,7, like her stealing from businesses.     
OL,9,FShe said shoplifting was easy, and even
OL,10,Fthe clothes she had on were stolen.    
OL,12,FBBC News has been speaking to shops who
OL,13,Fare blighted by shoplifting - as well  
OL,14,Fas those who are committing crimes.    
OL,16,FIt comes as retail bosses say they are 
OL,17,Fnow losing millions of pounds to       
OL,18,Fthefts, which are being driven by      
OL,19,Forganised crime gangs as well as       
OL,20,Fpersistent thieves.                    
